    ('03d4a47c-eeba-40ac-a5d3-112394c1fc43', 'Cross-Over Jack', 'The cross-over jack is a variation on the jumping jack, a popular calisthenics exercise used to improve overall conditioning. The difference between the jumping jack and the cross-over jack is that with the latter, the feet don''t just come together each rep, they cross over each other. It''s a great way to add variety to your warm-up or conditioning work.', 3, 3, 10, 8, 2, 'The difference between the jumping jack and the cross-over jack is that with the latter, the feet don''t just come together each rep, they cross over each other.', NULL, true, NULL, '2026-01-18 00:00:00.000 +0000'::timestamp with time zone, '[]'::text),
