    ('bd19d4bb-8909-48f1-a21d-5c91f8fc7ce1', 'Spider Curl', 'The EZ-bar spider curl is an exercise targeting the biceps and performed face down on either an incline bench or on the flat side of a preacher bench. The EZ-bar makes for a more comfortable wrist position, while the angle helps to isolate the biceps and limit involvement of the shoulder muscles. This curl variation is usually performed for moderate to high reps, such as 8-12 reps per set or more, as part of upper-body or arm-focused training.', 1, 2, 4, NULL, 2, 'The EZ-bar makes for a more comfortable wrist position, while the angle helps to isolate the biceps and limit involvement of the shoulder muscles.', NULL, true, NULL, '2026-01-18 00:00:00.000 +0000'::timestamp with time zone, '[{"Name": "Barbell", "IsRequired": true}, {"Name": "EZ-Bar", "IsRequired": true}]'::text),
    ('0cff4179-1361-4d26-839f-8230ed3708e5', 'Drag Curl', 'The drag curl is a biceps exercise that attempts to remove the influence of the front deltoids on the classic curl. With the elbows kept back, the barbell "drags" up the torso. It is usually performed for moderate to high reps, such as 8-15 reps per set, as part of an upper-body or arms-focused workout.', 1, 2, 4, NULL, 1, 'Perform drag curl with controlled movement, proper form, and full range of motion.', NULL, true, NULL, '2026-01-18 00:00:00.000 +0000'::timestamp with time zone, '[{"Name": "Barbell", "IsRequired": true}]'::text),
    ('735eca2e-c3ab-4df6-b0eb-95c8b5d9d9fb', 'Seated Straigh-Bar Curl Superset', 'The seated wide-grip curl to close-grip curl is a variation on the classic seated dumbbell curl. The variation is that the range of motion changes in alternating fashion—one more traditional, one where you’re bringing the weight in more from the side.', 1, 2, 4, NULL, 1, 'The seated wide-grip curl to close-grip curl is a variation on the classic seated dumbbell curl.', NULL, true, NULL, '2026-01-18 00:00:00.000 +0000'::timestamp with time zone, '[{"Name": "Barbell", "IsRequired": true}]'::text),
