    ('0ec3b0e3-a3f5-47ee-878d-3a96c179a94e', 'Suspended Press', 'The band-suspended kettlebell bench press is a bench press variation where kettlebells or weight plates are hung from the ends of a barbell by looped bands. The suspended weights can be in addition to normally loaded weight plates, or in the place of them. Because the instability of the weights makes the lift difficult, this bench press variety is a popular accessory movement for building the traditional bench press in powerlifting training.', 1, 1, 1, 5, 2, 'The band-suspended kettlebell bench press is a bench press variation where kettlebells or weight plates are hung from the ends of a barbell by looped bands. The suspended weights can be in addition to normally loaded weight plates, or in the place of them.', NULL, true, NULL, '2026-01-18 00:00:00.000 +0000'::timestamp with time zone, '[{"Name": "Band", "IsRequired": true}, {"Name": "Bench", "IsRequired": true}, {"Name": "Kettlebell", "IsRequired": true}, {"Name": "Resistance Band", "IsRequired": true}]'::text),
    ('5f599fdf-4a0f-4b1c-b22d-6e8106311d30', 'Close-Grip Press', 'The close-grip bench press is a popular exercise targeting the triceps and chest. The main difference between this exercise and the standard bench press is that the hands and elbows are placed closer together, which places more of an emphasis on the triceps. The close-grip bench press is often used as an accessory movement for the traditional bench press, or as a triceps builder for arm training. Similar to the bench press, it can be trained in low reps for strength or higher reps for muscle or strength endurance.', 1, 1, 1, 5, 2, 'The main difference between this exercise and the standard bench press is that the hands and elbows are placed closer together, which places more of an emphasis on the triceps. The close-grip bench press is often used as an accessory movement for the traditional bench press, or as a triceps builder for arm training.', NULL, true, NULL, '2026-01-18 00:00:00.000 +0000'::timestamp with time zone, '[{"Name": "Barbell", "IsRequired": true}, {"Name": "Bench", "IsRequired": true}]'::text),
